## Summary: 
Due to issue with the worklist & posting notes actions have been taken on THS & LUHS ARM databases.   Both databases have been scaled up in attempts keep users productive at the team troubleshoots the issues to find longer term solutions.   Due to scale change price has increased on both of these databases.

### Cost Breakdown
1 Vcore for 1 hour cost: $0.25

