| ---- | ------------ | -------------------- | ------------- | --------------------- |
| THS  | 18           | 4.5                  | 32            | 8                     |
| LUHS | 6            | 1.50                 | 14            | 3.5                   |

### Scale Schedule: 
M-F 
Servers scale up @ 5am
Server scale down @ 12:30 am


This can be adjusted to ANY time but we leave the window open because we do not have a shift schedule for the users in the site. I am happy to change this to ANY schedule we see fit. 


